      "message": "[Critical] Line 887: Resetting only `currentCameraZoom` leaves `CameraService.VideoParams.zoomRatio` unchanged, and `buildCaptureRequest()` reapplies that stored zoom on the next preview/session rebuild. This contradicts the comment and can restart the local preview still zoomed while the UI state thinks it is at 1x. Apply the reset to the hardware service as well when the preview is restarted/stopped, e.g.:\n```suggestion\nstopCameraProgressiveZoom()\ncurrentCameraZoom \u003d mHardwareService.setCurrentCameraZoom(1f)\n```",
      "revId": "a9c3ae8eae54bdb6e0ef53fcb48d01be11fd7fb9",
